form:combobox.form:list-source: select distinct Anrede from Kunden order by Anrede ASC
select distinct Titel from Kunden order by Titel ASC

form:listbox.form:list-source: select distinct year(t1.Erstellungsdatum),year(t1.Erstellungsdatum) as Jahr from (Rechnungen1 as t1, Gutschriften1 as t2) INNER JOIN Steuerung as t3 ON t3.ClientID=22 where (t1.KontaktID=t3.KontaktID OR t2.KontaktID=t3.KontaktID) order by Jahr DESC

form:combobox.form:list-source: select distinct Anrede from Ansprechpartner_Kunden order by Anrede ASC
select distinct Titel from Ansprechpartner_Kunden order by Titel ASC

form:listbox.form:list-source: select distinct concat(t1.Name1,', ',t1.Vorname,' ',t1.Name2,' --> ',t1.Ort) as Name, t1.KontaktID from Kunden as t1 INNER JOIN Steuerung as t2 ON ClientID=22 where ((((t1.Name1 like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Vorname like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Name2 like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Name3 like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Name4 like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Land like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.PLZ like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Ort like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Strasse like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Hausnummer like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Mindestangaben like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Telefon like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Funktelefon like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Fax like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.EMail like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Url like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Aquise like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.Bemerkungen like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') or t1.ReferenzID like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%')) and t2.Suchstring IS NOT NULL)) or (t1.Name1 like '%' and t2.Suchstring IS NULL)) order by t1.Name1 ASC
